parallel.distributed

Class DConditionCounterLLCClt

  • java.lang.Object
    • parallel.distributed.DConditionCounterLLCClt

  • public class DConditionCounterLLCClt
extends java.lang.Object
    Same functionality as DConditionCounter[Clt|Srv] classes, but use long-lived connections, for clients that call frequently incr/decr ops. When no longer needed, client must call closeConnection().

    Title: popt4jlib

    Description: A Parallel Meta-Heuristic Optimization Library in Java

    Copyright: Copyright (c) 2011-2016

    Company:

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ioannis T. Christou
